	dprr:hasNoteText "Named with Agrippa (see below) as one of Octavian's commanders in the Illyrian war (App. Illyr. 20, without title), so strange a name in such a connection that Nero has been suggested (RE), since Ti . Claudius Nero survived until 33 (Suet. Tib. 6)." .
